planning/budget/description: Budget allocation for highway maintenance, aligned with 2015 strategic plan.
planning/rationale: The 2009 Strategic Plan identifies a need for an improved cycle route in the centre of town.
tender/description: The authority plans to tender for improvements to the cycle lane in early 2010. This notice provides advanced notice of the intention to tender, and details to upcoming consultation events.
tender/procurementMethodDetails: In open procedures, any interested economic operator may submit a tender in response to a contract notice.
tender/procurementMethodRationale: An open competitive tender is required by EU Rules
tender/awardCriteriaDetails: The best proposal, subject to value for money requirements, will be accepted.
